# Assign Collision Group

## Description

Assigns a BasePart to a collision group.

#### Available to

* [x] Scripts
* [x] LocalScripts
* [ ] Yields

## Inputs

#### GroupName (String)

The first collision group's name.

* [x] Can use Variable

```
BlacklistParts
```

#### BasePart (Object)

The path of the part object.

* [x] Can use Variable

```
game.Workspace.BlacklistedPart
```
